Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.52,0:04:17.77,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ　この弔問に訪れた国民の数を見れば分かる
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.57,0:04:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. This is evident by the number of citizens who came to mourn him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.86,0:04:22.65,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,王は父親として立派な責務を果たされたな
