Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.50,0:04:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,So, even prodigal prince moved to tears by his father's death.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.05,0:04:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And here you have a little bit wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.06,0:04:50.81,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,それも少し違うな
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.15,0:04:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,This man - a born hypocrite.
