Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.61,0:05:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Jaswant, that you are now going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.78,0:05:46.61,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,これからどうするつもりなのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.90,0:05:49.20,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,さて　どうしましょうか
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.91,0:05:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, what can I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.66,0:05:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,In this realm I no longer have a place.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.70,0:05:52.87,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,もはやこの国に私の居場所はありませぬ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.82,0:05:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, the fact is that I am just like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.87,0:06:00.00,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,実は私もな　お主と同じなのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.31,0:06:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Same?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.38,0:06:01.21,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,同じ？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.79,0:06:06.47,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,私の父上と母上は本当の両親ではないらしい
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.83,0:06:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,My mother and father are not my real parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.54,0:06:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And, perhaps, the highest position of the Prince Parsis do not belong to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.55,0:06:12.47,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,私はパルスの王子なんて偉い身分ではないのかもしれないのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.14,0:06:16.98,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,だが　ダリューンやナルサスたちは　それでも私についてきてくれる
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.16,0:06:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,But Daryun, Narsus and others continue to believe in me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.10,0:06:21.02,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,私もその思いに応えたいと思っている
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.11,0:06:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And I want to earn that trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.82,0:06:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you coming with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.82,0:06:27.36,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,お主も一緒に来てはくれないだろうか
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.30,0:06:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.36,0:06:30.24,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,あなたは…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.03,0:06:37.08,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,そこがお主の新しい居場所になればいいとそう思っている
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.04,0:06:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope that you find a new place.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.85,0:06:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.84,0:06:45.96,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,おお　アルスラーン殿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.64,0:06:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince Arslan, there you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.96,0:06:47.51,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ここにおられたか
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.96,0:06:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,King Rajendra. How can I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.01,0:06:50.84,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ラジェンドラ殿　何か御用でしょうか
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.59,0:06:56.43,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,昨日の今日で申し訳ないが　今宵　宴を開く運びとなった
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.61,0:06:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry about yesterday,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.93,0:06:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,but tonight will be a banquet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.07,0:06:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I ask you to attend as a guest?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.14,0:06:59.89,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,国賓として出席してはいただけないか
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.24,0:07:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Banquet? In honor of what?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.31,0:07:02.65,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,宴？　一体なんの
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.37,0:07:17.79,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,どういうことだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.45,0:07:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What does it mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.45,0:07:21.37,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ガーデーヴィは王族とはいえ　反逆者であろう
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.48,0:07:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Gadevi though of the royal family, but he betrayed the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.67,0:07:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Former Prince sindoor, Gadevi
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.68,0:07:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And yet, and a banquet in his honor?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.71,0:07:23.54,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,それを囲んで宴など…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.96,0:07:25.21,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,聞いたことがある
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.98,0:07:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.71,0:07:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,In sindoor on the occasion of the royal treasury
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.75,0:07:31.34,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,シンドゥラでは王族を処刑する際　酒と料理を存分に振る舞うのだとな
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.37,0:07:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,they treated the condemned food and wine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.51,0:07:33.72,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,なるほど
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.59,0:07:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.01,0:07:39.02,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,苦しまぬよう　酔い潰れて正体を失ったところを殺すというわけか
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.03,0:07:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,To save him from suffering,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.20,0:07:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Man will be killed immediately, as soon as he gets drunk to unconsciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.02,0:07:44.19,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,これがガーデーヴィにとって　人生最後の宴か
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.08,0:07:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,For Gadevi this last banquet in his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.99,0:07:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up, brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.02,0:07:48.36,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,どうした　兄上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.27,0:07:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Something you drink enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.28,0:07:52.03,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,杯が進んでいないようだが
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.70,0:07:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The ruler of the kingdom sindoor, Rajendra
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.91,0:07:56.37,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,認めたくはない… が
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.94,0:07:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I do not want to admit it, but ...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.20,0:08:01.08,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ラジェンドラ　やはり　お前の勝ちのようだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.22,0:08:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Rajendra seems, still you win.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.63,0:08:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.29,0:08:08.13,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,私はお前の配下となろう
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.29,0:08:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be your servant.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.65,0:08:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And I swear allegiance to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.67,0:08:10.51,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,お前に忠誠を誓う
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.72,0:08:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Just ... keep me alive, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.72,0:08:14.09,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,だから　私を生かしておいてくれるな
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.89,0:08:19.22,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,情けない命乞いなどしてくれるな
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.94,0:08:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not beg for the life of such a pathetic manner.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.71,0:08:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We are half-brothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.72,0:08:22.69,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,俺たちは血を分けた兄弟だろう
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.19,0:08:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Z-means ...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.23,0:08:24.65,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,で…では…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.69,0:08:31.03,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,パルスの王太子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.70,0:08:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Crown Prince Parsis!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.44,0:08:33.61,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,アルスラーン殿がいらっしゃったぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.52,0:08:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince Arslan came!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.28,0:08:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince Lions!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.61,0:08:35.57,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,アルスラーン殿だ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.99,0:08:40.87,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,パルスの小僧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.01,0:08:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Parsiansky kid ...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.70,0:08:45.21,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,思えば　ヤツが来てから全てが狂ったのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.71,0:08:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,If you think, after his arrival things went awry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.67,0:08:48.00,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,あの小僧さえ来なければ…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.68,0:08:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,If he had not come here ... if you did not have the support ...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.09,0:08:50.50,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,貴様に手を貸さなければ…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.88,0:08:54.55,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,静まれ　ガーデーヴィ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.90,0:08:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Uspokoysya, Gadevi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.55,0:08:55.68,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,うるさい
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.57,0:08:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.48,0:09:05.23,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,疫病神め　思い知れ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.54,0:09:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Distributor of failure, you'll pay!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.18,0:09:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I do not expect that you would be so disgusting, defeated.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.20,0:09:24.71,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ここまで未練なヤツとはな
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.16,0:09:28.58,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,あの世で父上に性根を鍛え直していただけ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.18,0:09:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Let the father corrects you in that light.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.88,0:09:34.26,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,放せ　無礼者が
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.99,0:09:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go! Arrogant idiots!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.90,0:09:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.97,0:09:38.55,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,殺れ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.93,0:09:41.31,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,や…やめ…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.49,0:09:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,C-stand! ..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.08,0:10:08.08,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ラジェンドラ殿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.11,0:10:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,King Rajendra.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.37,0:10:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,If you think we were brothers evil fruit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.42,0:10:13.80,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,思えば　俺たちは不幸な兄弟だった
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.38,0:10:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,If we were not relatives, we might better get along.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.42,0:10:19.22,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,いっそ他人同士なら　もっと仲よくなれたかもしれんな
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.72,0:10:21.80,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,本当に残念です
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.76,0:10:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.87,0:10:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you did a lot for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.89,0:10:26.35,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,いや　お主には本当に世話になった
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.69,0:10:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I am thankful.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.73,0:10:27.64,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,感謝する
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.56,0:10:34.86,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ところで　アルスラーン殿はそろそろパルスへ戻られるのだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.58,0:10:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, you're soon back in Parsa Prince Arslan?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.32,0:10:37.90,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ええ　明日にはここをたつつもりです
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.34,0:10:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I am going to go tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.20,0:10:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,And nakonets expel Lyusitaniyu, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.20,0:10:41.49,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,そして　いよいよルシタニアを追い払う…か
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.78,0:10:42.37,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.79,0:10:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.07,0:10:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,If I were a strategist Lyusitanii,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.12,0:10:48.91,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,俺がルシタニアの軍師なら　まずは隣国に使者を送るなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.29,0:10:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,first would have sent envoys to neighboring kingdoms.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.04,0:10:50.71,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,隣国に…　ですか
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.08,0:10:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,In the neighboring kingdoms?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.00,0:10:54.42,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,東方のチュルク　そして北東のトゥラーン
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.02,0:10:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The Turk in the east and Turan in the north-east.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.64,0:10:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I am persuaded each of them to break the boundaries of Parsis.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.67,0:10:58.51,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,それらを唆して　パルス国境を侵させる
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.26,0:11:02.97,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,その隙に　ルシタニアは背後から私たちを襲う
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.29,0:11:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,And with this breach Lyusitaniya would attack us from the rear.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.10,0:11:05.18,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,どうだ　俺の読みは
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.13,0:11:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you like my ability to count steps?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.41,0:11:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Narsus recently spoke about the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.43,0:11:08.68,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,はい　ナルサスも以前　同じことを申しておりました
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.39,0:11:12.90,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ならば　俺もお主の軍師になれるかもしれぬな
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.50,0:11:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Then maybe I can also serve you a strategist.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.44,0:11:18.61,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ですが　ナルサスはそれに対抗する手段も７つほど思いついているとか
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.62,0:11:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,But Narsus also mentioned that has left about seven options to rebuff them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.69,0:11:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,With seven ?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.69,0:11:19.99,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,な…７つ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.28,0:11:21.66,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,はい　７つです
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.34,0:11:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, the semi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.11,0:11:25.49,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,聞かせてくれ　それは一体どんな策なのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.31,0:11:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I would like to hear what kind of tactics.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.68,0:11:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,He did not talk about them, even to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.70,0:11:28.79,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,それ以上は　私にも教えてくれませんでした
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.25,0:11:30.41,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,秘中の秘だそうです
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.28,0:11:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently, this is sensitive information.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.46,0:11:36.38,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,まっ　そんな話はいい
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.51,0:11:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, forget about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.75,0:11:38.42,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,前に約束したな
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.75,0:11:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I have already given an oath.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.61,0:11:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That in exchange for your help me, I'll help you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.63,0:11:44.35,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,お主が俺に力を貸してくれる代わりに　俺もお主に力を貸してやると
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.72,0:11:45.14,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.74,0:11:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.47,0:11:47.51,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,今こそ　それを果たすときだ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.48,0:11:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And the hour to fulfill this promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.80,0:11:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I owe you a great debt.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.81,0:11:49.73,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,お主には多大な恩がある
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.81,0:11:52.44,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,俺にできることなら　なんでも協力するぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.83,0:11:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I will do everything in my power.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.99,0:11:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just the earth can not give.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.02,0:11:55.15,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,領土だけは譲れんがな
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.31,0:11:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Treasures or provisions ...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.40,0:11:59.11,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,財宝でも糧食でも…　それとも美女がいいかな
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.53,0:11:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Or do you want beautiful women?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.44,0:12:00.32,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,そうですか
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.44,0:12:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.78,0:12:05.07,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,では　兵を５００ほどお貸しください
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.80,0:12:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Then give me five hundred soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.94,0:12:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Soldier? Only five hundred?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.95,0:12:06.83,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,兵を？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.20,0:12:10.00,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,たったの５００　水くさいことを
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.61,0:12:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Pray as if we were strangers! It's you and I!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.04,0:12:14.58,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,俺とお主の仲だろう　３０００騎　貸してやろうではないか
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.13,0:12:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do not you ask for three thousand horsemen?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.85,0:12:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's too ...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.88,0:12:16.63,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,い…いえ　そこまでは…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.63,0:12:18.50,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,いや　３０００だ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.66,0:12:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Three thousand.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.54,0:12:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And do not embarrass me, Rajendra.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.55,0:12:21.26,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,このラジェンドラに恥をかかせんでくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.97,0:12:26.14,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,そこまでおっしゃるのでしたら　お言葉に甘えさせていただきます
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.07,0:12:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,If you insist, I am pleased to accept this gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.55,0:12:30.10,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ　俺たちは心の兄弟だからな
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.61,0:12:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. We're brothers in spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.81,0:12:37.65,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,何をお考えなのですか
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.96,0:12:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You are what you think ?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.92,0:12:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Three thousand - is in any case too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.98,0:12:40.65,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,いくらなんでも　３０００騎は多すぎます
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.82,0:12:44.86,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,まだシンドゥラ国内も完全に平定されたとは言えないのですぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.84,0:12:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We still can not even claim
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.22,0:12:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,that there is peace on the borders sindoor.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.03,0:12:47.20,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,こんなときに貴重な戦力を…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.09,0:12:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And at this time you spread: a valuable force ...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.20,0:12:48.49,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,分からんか
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.23,0:12:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.12,0:12:51.08,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,３０００騎は火種よ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.13,0:12:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,These three thousand - the material for kindling.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.44,0:12:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,To burn to ashes army Parsis.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.45,0:12:54.12,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,パルスの軍を焼き尽くすためのな
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.26,0:12:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.33,0:12:55.42,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,なんですと
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.50,0:12:58.17,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ダリューンらがいかに一騎当千でも
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.52,0:12:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,However powerful may be Daryun and his company,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.34,0:13:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,they will not last long if they are to break from the inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.42,0:13:01.63,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,内部から突き崩されれば　ひとたまりもあるまい
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.71,0:13:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It already moves the border ...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.71,0:13:03.55,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,それはあまりにも…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.61,0:13:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,They also help you to get the throne!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.63,0:13:06.51,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,彼らは殿下の即位に手を貸してくれたのですぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.14,0:13:08.89,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,だからこそさ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.20,0:13:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That is why.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.51,0:13:13.31,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,俺はな　あの甘ちゃん王子が好きなのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.52,0:13:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, I like the sentimental prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.81,0:13:15.85,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,こんな策を弄するのも
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.84,0:13:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I resort to such dirty tricks,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.94,0:13:20.69,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,あの坊やに国王として大きく成長してもらいたいからさ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.00,0:13:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,because I want the little boy has grown rapidly worthy ruler.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.34,0:13:50.93,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,そういえば　あいつ　どうしたかな
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.40,0:13:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what happened to that jerk?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.00,0:13:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,With that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.01,0:13:51.81,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,あいつ？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.84,0:13:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,With Jaswant. After all, he did not go with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.89,0:13:53.10,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ジャスワントだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.39,0:13:55.68,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,結局　ついてこなかったんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.93,0:13:57.31,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ　そうじゃな
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.53,0:13:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.56,0:13:58.85,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,いいんじゃないですか
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.59,0:13:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, let.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.15,0:14:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,After all that has happened, we can not trust him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.19,0:14:01.82,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,今更　信用できませんよ　あんなヤツ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.14,0:14:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think the soldiers sindoor, which we singled out the king Rajendra?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.19,0:14:09.70,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,どうだ　ラジェンドラ王から借り受けたシンドゥラ兵たちの様子は
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.58,0:14:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You are the people of General Kuntavaya?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.62,0:14:12.70,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,クンタヴァー将軍の隊か
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.23,0:14:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,They are well trained.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.24,0:14:15.20,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,よく統率されているな
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.79,0:14:18.17,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,こちらの指示にも素直に従ってくれる
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.83,0:14:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And follow all our instructions.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.38,0:14:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,General sindoor, Kuntavay
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.71,0:14:21.09,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,あの様子なら　即戦力になりそうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.77,0:14:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,They can be a good help in the fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.42,0:14:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.42,0:14:22.21,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,そうか
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.54,0:14:24.21,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,それならばいいがな
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.56,0:14:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,If so, then okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.92,0:14:29.38,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,殿下　そろそろ日が暮れます
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.00,0:14:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince, the sun will soon sit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.75,0:14:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's break camp here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.76,0:14:31.43,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,この辺りで　陣を張りましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.48,0:15:25.69,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,始まったようです
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.51,0:15:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems to have started.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.48,0:15:30.20,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,クンタヴァーめ　首尾よくやってくれたようだな
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.55,0:15:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The cunning old man Kuntavay. It seems that he will succeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.20,0:15:34.49,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,行くぞ　俺に続け
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.32,0:15:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Forward! All over me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.37,0:15:41.46,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,アルスラーンは殺すなよ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.41,0:15:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Arlsana not kill!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.90,0:15:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Taken hostage and brought to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.92,0:15:44.38,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,人質にして俺のところに連れてこい
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.25,0:15:48.01,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,な…なんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.39,0:15:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What?..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.46,0:15:52.22,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,なんだ　これは…　どういうことだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.48,0:15:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.06,0:15:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.39,0:15:55.55,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,クンタヴァー
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.42,0:15:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Kuntavay!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.81,0:16:01.35,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,シンドゥラの横着者よ　お主の奸計はすでに破れた
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.87,0:15:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Sinduriansky impudent scoundrel!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.21,0:16:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Your cunning conspiracy has long been unmasked!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.89,0:16:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.90,0:16:03.98,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,しまった…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.19,0:16:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It is a trap! Retreat, retreat!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.19,0:16:06.86,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,罠だ　退け　退け
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.61,0:16:14.36,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,撃て
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.91,0:16:23.25,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ラジェンドラ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.93,0:16:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Rajendra!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.35,0:16:40.97,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,うちの軍師殿は全てお見通しだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.37,0:16:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. our tactics all foreseen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.43,0:16:45.15,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,知恵者面はシンドゥラの中だけにしておくんだな
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.46,0:16:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to stay sly fox, would have remained in sindoor.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.77,0:16:48.86,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,おのれ…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.84,0:16:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh you!..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.82,0:16:59.24,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,アルスラーン王太子の臣下として　ここを通すわけにはまいりませぬ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.85,0:16:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,As a devoted maid Crown Prince Arslan I will not let you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.46,0:17:07.75,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,やれやれ　ここまでか
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.50,0:17:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, well, it looks like this is the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.13,0:17:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Not in my spirit harm beautiful women.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.17,0:17:12.05,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,美しい女性を傷つけるのは俺の本意ではない
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.88,0:17:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,King Rajendra ...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.89,0:17:19.93,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ラジェンドラ殿…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.68,0:17:25.27,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,そんな顔をするな　元来　戦とはこういうものよ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.74,0:17:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not look at me like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.84,0:17:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, in fact, runs the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.93,0:17:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,But how did you manage to see through my plot?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.98,0:17:30.77,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,だが　どうやって俺の策を見破ったのかな
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.06,0:17:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's still you, Jaswant.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.07,0:17:35.65,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,やはりお前か
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.11,0:17:37.11,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ジャスワント
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.40,0:17:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I collected all the details that were known about you,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.41,0:17:40.95,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,おおかた動きは読めてはいたが
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.22,0:17:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,but thanks to his warning made sure of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.24,0:17:44.29,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,彼が知らせてくれたおかげで　確信が持てた
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.19,0:17:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.29,0:17:49.04,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,殿下…　いや　新たな王よ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.21,0:17:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,No. My new king
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.87,0:17:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I tell you this as a servant sindoor.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.88,0:17:52.34,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,シンドゥラの民の一人として申し上げる
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.26,0:17:55.80,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,これ以上の醜態をさらされるな
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.30,0:17:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not disgrace myself even more.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.59,0:18:00.22,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,シンドゥラの民としてか
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.62,0:18:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Sindoor as a servant, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.47,0:18:06.56,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,そう言われては　返す言葉もない
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.49,0:18:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,To this I even have nothing to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.50,0:18:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Insolent bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.69,0:18:10.86,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,この恥知らずが
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.69,0:18:12.40,UP JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,恩を仇で返すとは
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.80,0:18:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,This is how you repay the aid ?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.40,0:18:14.32,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,恥を知れ　蛮族め
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.48,0:18:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I am ashamed, barbarian!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.82,0:18:20.32,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,やれやれだ…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.85,0:18:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Gee.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.57,0:18:23.58,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,お主の捕虜になるのは　これで二度目だな
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.59,0:18:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I was the second time become your prisoner.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.01,0:18:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, å at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.08,0:18:25.45,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,そうなりますね
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.97,0:18:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what are you going to do with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.00,0:18:29.00,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,さて　俺をどうするつもりだ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.17,0:18:30.67,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,今度こそ殺すかい
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.18,0:18:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.92,0:18:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I will save lives and get you in Parsa
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.96,0:18:33.88,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,いえ　あなたはこのままパルスに連れ帰り
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.92,0:18:35.67,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,しばらく滞在していただきます
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.94,0:18:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,where you pobudet some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.29,0:18:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, two years.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.34,0:18:38.34,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,そうですね…　２年ほど
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.35,0:18:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Two years? It looks like a lot of fun waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.43,0:18:42.60,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,２年か　たっぷり楽しめそうだな
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.89,0:18:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And one more thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.89,0:18:44.51,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,それともう一つ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.22,0:18:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,N-Narsus ...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.22,0:18:46.85,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ナ…ナルサス
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.50,0:18:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What you have in mind this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.52,0:18:50.98,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,お主　今度は一体　何を企んでいる
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.46,0:18:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I decided to send a letter signed by you,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.48,0:18:56.07,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,このことは近隣の諸国にも親書でお知らせしようかと思います
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.81,0:18:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,to notify the neighbors of this fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.19,0:18:56.78,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,何
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.25,0:18:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.32,0:19:00.70,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ひとまず東方のチュルク　それに北東のトゥラーン
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.39,0:19:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,First, in the Turk in the east, then to Turan in the north-east.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.99,0:19:02.45,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,おい　やめろ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.99,0:19:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not that! Turk has long had his eye on the ground sindoor!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.45,0:19:05.79,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,チュルクは以前からシンドゥラの領土を狙っているんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.94,0:19:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,If they find out ...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.99,0:19:07.50,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,もし　ヤツらに知られたら…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.04,0:19:09.37,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,驚くでしょうね
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.10,0:19:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,They are just surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.84,0:19:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,King sindoor just ascended the throne,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.87,0:19:13.71,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,即位したばかりのシンドゥラ王がいきなり不在とは
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.33,0:19:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,suddenly he went out somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.89,0:19:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Please do not!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.92,0:19:15.17,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,やめてくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.30,0:19:16.76,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなことをしたら
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.49,0:19:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,If you do,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.76,0:19:20.13,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,２年後に俺が帰る国がなくなってしまうではないか
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.82,0:19:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,two years will not be of that kingdom, where I can go back!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.30,0:19:23.64,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,では　改めて不可侵条約を結び
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.36,0:19:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Then again you enclose a non-aggression pact
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.76,0:19:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and swear Pars leave alone for the next three years. Going?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.80,0:19:28.23,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,今後３年の間は　パルスに手を出さないと誓っていただけますか
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.64,0:19:30.60,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,３年か…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.71,0:19:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Three years...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.73,0:19:37.03,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ　誓う　誓う
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.73,0:19:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear, I swear!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.16,0:19:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear, you hear? I swear!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.19,0:19:38.86,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,誓えばいいんだろう　誓えば
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.68,0:19:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Narsus can question?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.71,0:19:57.96,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ねえ　ナルサス　一つ聞いていい
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.55,0:19:59.05,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,なんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.56,0:19:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.42,0:20:00.76,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,なぜ３年なの
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.54,0:20:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Why three years?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.17,0:20:04.85,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,どうせなら　５０年…１００年にしておけばよかったのに
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.26,0:20:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Better would require fifty ... a hundred years better immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.05,0:20:06.68,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,そこまで長期となると
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.13,0:20:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Such long term
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.95,0:20:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Rajendra will be for eternity.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.97,0:20:10.02,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ラジェンドラにとっては　もはや永遠と同義だろう
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.73,0:20:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And the villain will not wait so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.73,0:20:13.31,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,あの横着者が辛抱できるはずもない
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.56,0:20:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.56,0:20:14.65,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,なるほどね
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.16,0:20:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And in three years he will keep himself in hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.19,0:20:19.23,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,３年程度なら　まだ我慢しようという気にもなる…　か
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.73,0:20:24.07,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし　その間にヤツはシンドゥラを完全に平定し
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.78,0:20:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,But during this time, he will establish order in sindoor
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.20,0:20:26.49,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,またパルスに攻め込んでくるだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.21,0:20:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,and be sure to again attack the Pars.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.78,0:20:27.45,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.79,0:20:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, we must banish the Prince Lyusitaniyu until
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.83,0:20:31.87,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,だから　我々は…　殿下はそれまでにルシタニアを追い払い
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.20,0:20:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,and return the royal capital.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.25,0:20:34.21,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,王都を奪還しなくてはならない
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.25,0:20:39.00,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.28,0:20:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.09,0:20:40.71,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ダリューン
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.13,0:20:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Darjun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.18,0:20:45.26,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,やはり私はあの御仁を…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.24,0:20:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I still can not hate him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.80,0:20:48.93,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ラジェンドラ殿を　どうしても憎むことができないのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.81,0:20:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hating King Rajendra impossible ...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.42,0:20:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm too lenient with these people?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.48,0:20:55.90,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,私の考えは甘いだろうか
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.73,0:21:01.23,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,アンドラゴラス三世陛下でしたら
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.77,0:21:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether in your place Andragoras King III,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.49,0:21:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,he would never forgive him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.49,0:21:04.11,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,あの男を決してお許しにはなりますまい
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.65,0:21:05.78,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,そうだろうな
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.80,0:21:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That's for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.80,0:21:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But the Prince, you are you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.87,0:21:07.70,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ですが　殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.70,0:21:10.20,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,あなたはあなたです
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.91,0:21:13.87,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,父上の考え方まで継ぐ必要はありません
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.92,0:21:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You do not have to go down the same path as that of your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.63,0:21:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Darjun.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.71,0:21:15.37,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ダリューン
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.44,0:21:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And we made a pact of non-aggression.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.46,0:21:18.63,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,不可侵条約もありますしね
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.01,0:21:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,For a while he did not finds itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.04,0:21:21.17,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,しばらくは　おとなしくしていますよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.49,0:21:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.55,0:21:22.30,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,みんな
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.64,0:21:28.68,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ジャスワント
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.74,0:21:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Jaswant.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.14,0:21:35.77,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,俺はシンドゥラ人です
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.19,0:21:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I sindurianets.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.35,0:21:39.23,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,もし　またパルスとシンドゥラが戦うことがあれば
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.37,0:21:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,If Parsa and sindoor again come together in battle,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.81,0:21:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I stand on the side of the country and will fight against the Parsis.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.81,0:21:42.48,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,俺は故郷に付いて　パルスと戦います
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.14,0:21:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.19,0:21:43.74,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,お前…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.52,0:21:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But the prince saved my life three times already in different cases.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.57,0:21:49.16,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ですが　俺は三度にわたって　殿下に命を救っていただきました
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.71,0:21:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,While I do not repay him for it ...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.78,0:21:52.12,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,その借りを返させていただくまで…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.29,0:21:55.91,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,アルスラーン王太子殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.37,0:21:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Crown Prince Arslan,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.67,0:22:01.25,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,このジャスワント　改めてあなたにお仕えすることを誓います
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.71,0:22:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I have, Jaswant officially swear to serve you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.58,0:22:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, they work.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.59,0:22:03.55,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ　よろしく頼む
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.09,0:22:09.64,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,新たなる仲間を得て
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.11,0:22:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Upon receipt of a new friend
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.01,0:22:13.77,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,アルスラーンの初めての国外遠征は終わりを告げた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.05,0:22:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,the first foreign military campaign Arslan came to an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.69,0:22:20.27,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,パルス暦３２１年２月半ば
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.75,0:22:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The era of Parsis, the middle of February 321 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.10,0:22:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Theater of war shifted again on earth Parsis.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.11,0:22:24.57,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,戦いの舞台は　再びパルスへと戻る
